write_up: Tyler, The Creator might be the most widely recognizable rapper of the decade. Most kids know who he is, even if they don’t listen to music. He’s always been a prodigious producer, but SMUCKERS shows another side, the ‘Kanye’ conductor touch, building a unique scene, inviting great rappers into it (like Kanye), while he follows his own one of a kind artistic instincts.
song: SMUCKERS (ft. Lil Wayne and Kanye West)
